mal; text-align:center; font-size:17px;"><span style="font-family:lato-light,lato,sans-serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="color_36 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Farmers</span></span></span></p></div><div id="comp-m7bpioip" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-m7bpioip wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; text-align:center; font-size:17px;"><span style="font-family:lato-light,lato,sans-serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="color_36 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">1,000+</span></span></span></p></div><div id="comp-m7bpioj4" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-m7bpioj4 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; text-align:center; font-size:17px;"><span style="font-family:lato-light,lato,sans-serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="color_36 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">&nbsp;CBOs</span></span></span></p></div></div></div></div><div id="comp-m7bpbdcg" class="comp-m7bpbdcg YzqVVZ wixui-column-strip__column"><div id="bgLayers_comp-m7bpbdcg" data-hook="bgLayers" data-motion-part="BG_LAYER comp-m7bpbdcg" class="MW5IWV"><div data-testid="colorUnderlay" class="LWbAav Kv1aVt"></div><div id="bgMedia_comp-m7bpbdcg" data-motion-part="BG_MEDIA comp-m7bpbdcg" class="VgO9Yg"></div></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-m7bpbdcginlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-m7bpbdcginlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><div id="comp-m7bpl5ai" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-m7bpl5ai wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:36px; line-height:normal; text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:36px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:lato-light,lato,sans-serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="color_36 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Upcoming Event</span></span></span></span></p></div><div id="comp-m7bpo5hw" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-m7bpo5hw wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; text-align:center; font-size:17px;"><span style="font-family:lato-light,lato,sans-serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="color_36 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">The CSR/CSO&rsquo;s Conclave &ndash; South India 2026 is a two-day regional event focused on environmental sustainability, climate change, and sustainable practices. It is organized by FEVOURD-K in collaboration with Vishwa Yuvak Kendra (VYK) and will be held on 7th and 8th January 2026 at Golden Metro Hotel, Sheshadripuram, Bengaluru.</span></span></span></p></div><div class="comp-m7bpp1ud FubTgk" id="comp-m7bpp1ud" aria-disabled="false"><a data-testid="linkElement" href="https://www.fevourd-k.org/ministries" target="_self" class="uDW_Qe wixui-button PlZyDq" aria-disabled="false" aria-label="Read More"><span class="l7_2fn wixui-button__label">Read More</span></a></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></section><section id="comp-lt8rm5hb1" tabindex="-1" class="Oqnisf comp-lt8rm5hb1 wixui-section" data-block-level-container="ClassicSection"><div id="bgLayers_comp-lt8rm5hb1" data-hook="bgLayers" data-motion-part="BG_LAYER comp-lt8rm5hb1" class="MW5IWV"><div data-testid="colorUnderlay" class="LWbAav Kv1aVt"></div><div id="bgMedia_comp-lt8rm5hb1" data-motion-part="BG_MEDIA comp-lt8rm5hb1" class="VgO9Yg"></div></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-lt8rm5hb1inlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-